| `BLOCK_SIZE` / `BLOCK_PREMIUM` | Block discount threshold and price | Names are clear. |
| `BASE_PREMIUM` | Map of item type to individual base premium | Clear. |
| `PROCESSING_FEE` / `FIRST_INSURANCE_RATE` | Fee and rate constants | Clear. |

Decision: Keep current names. `processScenario` is slightly generic but the function's scope will grow as more step types are added (claims, etc.), so renaming to something narrower now would require re-renaming later. All other names are clear and well-chosen.

## Step 2: Calculate Initial APP Mass

